wiki.content: According to the Come On Eileen Songfacts, Eileen was a girl that songwriter and band member Kevin Rowland grew up with. Their relationship became romantic when the pair were 13. The song describes the thin line between love and lust. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
